{"tid":2299770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港最壞時刻 五核心指標「肥佬」","createTime":"2020-11-25T04:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T04:40:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c40debd6471015cfc05d729050d83577d47ff249","tid":2299770,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:30:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/NKNY24W4L5BPLEPNOTNJAQEQ5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FNKNY24W4L5BPLEPNOTNJAQEQ5E%2F&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=ac1a4368\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FNKNY24W4L5BPLEPNOTNJAQEQ5E%2F&h=6c840956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/NKNY24W4L5BPLEPNOTNJAQEQ5E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港最壞時刻 五核心指標「肥佬」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/66B7SPP0HH9j8tNtRYZNUUCwGCs=/1352x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TCIVAWG7VNG6DDMHWAA6HX3APM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F66B7SPP0HH9j8tNtRYZNUUCwGCs%3D%2F1352x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTCIVAWG7VNG6DDMHWAA6HX3APM.jpg&h=01023ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鍾劍華指社會指標均貼近歷年來低位。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港民意研究計劃發表最新民調，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/O3TMG0kZqIZpwe3YqhZfjGO-tJg=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4U5LS4LRPFDT7AT3KOFIMX67UY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FO3TMG0kZqIZpwe3YqhZfjGO-tJg%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4U5LS4LRPFDT7AT3KOFIMX67UY.jpg&h=2a8b4774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■民研調查指本港自由、法治及民主等評分仍全不及格。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n倘DQ區議員勢再大跌<br />\n<br />\n香港民研本月中訪問了1,005名市民對核心社會指標的意見，以10分為滿分，自由得4.6分、繁榮4.6分、安定4.1分、法治4.1分和民主3.7分，其中自由和安定指數比上月同一調查微跌百分之0.1，其餘指數即使輕微上升，但幅度均不顯著。<br />\n<br />\n龔偉森認為，五項核心社會指標變化趨向平穩，反映社會接受了最壞的情況會發生，即使近月四名民主派議員被DQ、多名民主派議員被警方以特權法拘捕，法治指數均無明顯回落，代表市民普遍認為「最差都發生咗」，加上延任立會認受性不足，數字上沒有「震撼」效果。但他指，若然政府大規模DQ民主派區議員，法治和民主指數都有機會大幅下滑。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所副行政總裁鍾劍華補充，五項核心社會指標數字貼近歷年來低位，其中四個指標在過去多年都貼近七分，但過去一年大幅下跌，創下歷年來新低點。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZNuSN2aaGSC2MZieBJ8UpxdjeNc=/748x703/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WUDQBBYA2NH2XF2SBB6YJRJOVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZNuSN2aaGSC2MZieBJ8UpxdjeNc%3D%2F748x703%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWUDQBBYA2NH2XF2SBB6YJRJOVI.jpg&h=d04cd76e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e67ccf02ab40a6510df314c08ea5c42d25b30da7","tid":2299770,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3270b207c307b288c1765a00c862672505abd1","tid":2299770,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:35:21.000Z","msg":"So what<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d96f7bb7161181b628b5fc529b80bfdffb9acfc","tid":2299770,"uid":139848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:36:23.000Z","msg":"法治：較上月升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母升你老母"},{"pid":"3cebdc88d5952e2859ce6929c82e99a876eb002d","tid":2299770,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:40: